text: Cromwell is an unincorporated community in Ohio County, Kentucky, United States. The community is located on U.S. Route 231 southeast of Beaver Dam. Cromwell has a post office with ZIP code 42333, which opened on May 28, 1846. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Ohio County, Kentucky Category:Unincorporated communities in Kentucky
title: Cromwell, Kentucky
